comments: I loved Dr. Gould. Smart, funny, well spoken, engaging and a true professional in the field. Has high expectation and will not accept excuses or tardiness, but efforts will be rewarded. The more you open up, verbally and mentally, the more you will get out of class. Teaches about individuals, societies, history and international sexuality issues.
